<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.8.5">
<l>ōvāt tuyarpiṟavi yuṭpaṭamaṟ ṟevvevaiyum</l>
<l>mūvāt taṉimutalāy mūvulakuṅ kāvalōṉ</l>
<l>māvāki yāmaiyāy mīṉāki māṉiṭamān</l>
<l>tēvāti tēva perumāṉeṉ ṟīrttaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The guardian of the three worlds, being the unaging solitary base</l>
<l>of all other things including birth with undending misery,</l>
<l>who is animal, tortoise, fish [and] human</l>
<l>the great man, the god beyond gods is my saviour.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
